title: Utica defeats Cardington to open district title defense
text: Utica defeats Cardington to open district title defense Buy Photo Utica's Shelby Francis tips the ball past Cardington defenders. Utica defeated Cardington 3-1 in a a Division III first-round match on Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015, at Utica High School. They advance to host Columbus Academy at 2:30 on Saturday. Sara C.
